profile: Roy Furniture Repair & Refinishing is a small family owned and operated furniture wood shop that specialize in repairing, restoring and upholstering antique furniture. Roy has been involved in the trade for over a decade and we guarantee your satisfaction. Located in Brampton, Ontario we give complementary free estimates and also pick up and deliver furniture. Give us a call, we look forward to hearing from you!
service_area:
Restoration of furniture both antique and new.

Refinishing furniture.

Veneer repair.
